==命名==
三十酸可以在[[蜂蠟|蜂蠟]]中找到，所以得名蜂花酸<ref>{{cite web |url=https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/10471 |title=Triacontanoic acid |format= |date= |publisher=PubChem |accessdate= |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116092054/https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/10471 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而且，它是個[[碳鏈|碳鏈]]有三十個碳、只有[[碳-碳單鍵|碳-碳單鍵]]的[[直鏈羧酸|直鏈羧酸]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chemicalbook.com/ChemicalProductProperty_CN_CB4488721.htm|title=三戊酸C30:0 |format= |date=|publisher= Chemical Book |accessdate=}}</ref>，得名三十（烷）酸。

==性質==
三十酸雖然具有[[羧酸|羧酸]]的[[官能團|官能團]]，但是由於它具有很長的[[碳鏈|碳鏈]]，所以它非常[[疏水|疏水]]，而且不溶於[[水|水]]，呈[[中性|中性]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://hmdb.ca/metabolites/HMDB0030925 |title=Showing metabocard for Melissic acid A (HMDB0030925) |format= |date= |publisher=Human Metabolome Database |accessdate= |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027154912/https://hmdb.ca/metabolites/HMDB0030925 |dead-url=no }}</ref>正因爲它的[[疏水性|疏水性]]，它可以用作含[[塑膠|塑膠]]物質的[[塗層|塗層]]<ref>{{Patent|Land=DE|V-Nr=10100195|Titel=Wäßriger, effektgebender Beschichtungsstoff, Verfahren zu seiner Herstellung und seine Verwendung|V-Datum=2002-07-11|Erfinder=Egon Wegner, Frank Jansing}}</ref>。對環境、水源可能[[有害|有害]]。<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.basechem.org/chemical/3379|title=蜂花酸 Melissic Acid|format=|date=|publisher=物競數據庫|accessdate=|archive-date=2017-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828053857/http://www.basechem.org/chemical/3379|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==製備==
三十酸首先是由蠟中提取出來的。<ref name='Chibnall'>{{cite journal | title = The isolation of n-triacontanol from lucerne wax | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_biochemical-journal_1933_27_6/page/1885 | journal = Biochemical Journal | year = 1933 | first = Albert Charles | last = Chibnall |author2=Ernest Frank Williams |author3=Alfred Louis Latner |author4=Stephen Harvey Piper  | volume = 27 | issue = 6 | pages = 1885–1888| pmid = 16745314 | pmc = 1253114}}</ref>[[褐煤蠟|褐煤蠟]]中也有小量三十酸的存在，可適量提取。<ref>Robert Hegnauer: ''Chemotaxonomie der Pflanzen.'' 2001, Birkhäuser-Verlag, ISBN 3-7643-6269-3.</ref>

現代的三十酸可以從[[三十酸甲酯|三十酸甲酯]]等[[三十酸酯|三十酸酯]]加酸或加鹼[[水解|水解]]反應製備而成。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Journal of Organic Chemistry USSR (English Translation)|last=Odinokov, V. N.; Akhmetova, V. R.; Khasanov, Kh. D.; Abduvakhabov, A. A.; Tolstikov, G. A.|first=Journal of Organic Chemistry USSR (English Translation)|publisher=|year=1990|isbn=|location=|pages=1209 - 1210}}</ref> 亦可透過[[三十醇|三十醇]]或[[三十醛|三十醛]]加[[重鉻酸鉀|重鉻酸鉀]]等[[氧化劑|氧化劑]]生成三十酸，[[反應產率|反應產率]]約爲百分之六十六<ref>{{cite journal | title = Organoboranes for synthesis. 13. Simple, efficient syntheses of long-chain alcohols and carboxylic acids.| journal =  Tetrahedron  | year =1990| first = Brown| last = HC|author2=RR Iyer|author3=NG Bhat |author4=US Racherla|author5=CA Brown | volume =48| issue = 42  | pages =  9187 - 9194| pmid =14507223| pmc =}}</ref>。

三十酸也可以從[[沙旋覆花|沙旋覆花]]提取分離製得，為白色結晶性粉末（[[丙酮|丙酮]]）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=沙旋复花中的化学成分|url=http://www.jipb.net|accessdate=|author=陳傑、黃韶光、李芳桂、方聖鼎、陳嬿|date=|format=pdf|publisher=植物學報|language=中文|archive-date=2009-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501204258/http://www.jipb.net/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==反應==
三十酸具有一般[[羧酸|羧酸]]的通性，可以跟[[醇|醇]]發生[[酯化反應|酯化反應]]<ref>{{cite journal en
 | author = [[Hermann_Emil_Fischer|Emil Fischer]], Arthur Speier | title = Darstellung der Ester  | journal = Chemische Berichte | volume = 28| pages = 3252–3258 | year =1895| doi = 10.1002/cber.189502803176}}</ref> ，跟[[三氯化磷|三氯化磷]]和[[氨|氨]]發生[[氨化|氨化]]反應<ref>{{Cite book|title=Amide formation|last=E. Cheng, J. Chow, Y.F. Chow, A. Kai ,S.L.Lee,W.H. Wong|first=HKDSE Chemistry A Modern View|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>，生成相應的[[三十酸酯|三十酸酯]]或[[酰胺|酰胺]]。<ref name="#1"/>亦可用[[氫化鋁鋰|氫化鋁鋰]]等[[還原劑|還原劑]]把三十酸還原成[[正三十醇|正三十醇]]。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Reductiong using LiAlH<sub>4</sub>|last=E. Cheng, J. Chow, Y.F. Chow, A. Kai ,S.L.Lee,W.H. Wong|first=HKDSE Chemistry A Modern View|publisher=|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=}}</ref>
